    "id": 112,
    "text": "Physical symptoms\nTachycardia,JVP, oedena \nencephalopathy, dry \nmucomembrane , weak \npulses, decrease level of \nconsiosuness. \nInvestigations  \nRenal functions, \nElectrolytes,\nUrine sediments, \nAbdominal U/S,\nECG if K + is high \nClassify AKI stage \n(KDGO/AKIN)\n• Stage 1: creat x1.5 baseline, urine output <0.5 mls/kg/hour \n  for 6 hours \n• Stage 2: creat x2 baseline, urine output <0.5 mls/kg/hour \n  for 12 hours \n• Stage 3: creat >3x, creat >356 mmol/l, urine output \n  <0.5 mls /kg/hour for 24 hours \nConfirm AKI\nStage 3\nRefer for pediatrician/\nnephrologist in a center \nthat can perform RRT",
