    "conditions": [
      "monitoring"
    ],
    "content_type": "treatment_recommendation",
    "char_length": 1006,
    "word_count": 173
  },
  {
    "id": 173,
    "text": "14\nPregnancy \no\nAre you pregnant now? Do you think that there is a chance that \nyou might be pregnant? \no\nDo you have any children?  If yes, wh \nen did you last \ndeliver? \no\nHow many children do you have?  How many times have you \nbeen pregnant? \nDiet \no\nDo you like to add salt to your food?   \no\nHas your diet changed for any reason? \nSexual History/HIV Risk Factors \no\nAre you sexually active now? Do you have sex with more than \none partner? \no\nDo you use condoms?   \no\nHave you ever been tested for HIV? When was the last time you \nwere tested? \n1.2.1.3 Family History \n1.  Ask about the family history: \no\nHas anyone in your family been told they have a problem with \ntheir heart? \no\nDoes anyone have the same symptoms as you do (i.e. dyspnea, \nfatigue, edema)? \n \nIf yes, test for pregnancy!",
