    "text": "19\n1.2.4.1.2\nEchocardiography \nEchocardiographic  Finding \nClinical Interpretation \nEnlarged left and/or right ventricles \nCardiomyopathy \nValvularvegetation (mitral / aortic) \nRHD or endocarditis \nMitral Stenosis \nRHD \nPericardial effusion  \nTuberculous pericarditis \n***Please refer to the echocardiographic curriculum for greater detail*** \n1.2.4.1.1\nChest Radiography \nRadiographic  Finding \nEnlarged cardiac silhouette \nBlunting of costovertebral angle \nBilateral interstitial infiltrates  \nClinical Interpretation \nCardiomyopathy or pericardial effusion \nPleural effusion  \nPulmonary edema",
