    "text": "30\n1.2.8\nPOST-SURGICAL CARE \n1.2.8.1 Early Follow-Up \n \n1.  If any of the following are suspected, call the cardiologist and refer to \nthe district hospital: \no\nNew Heart Failure \no\nSternal Wound Infection and Dehiscence \no\nPericardial Tamponade \no\nEndocarditis \no\nNew Arrhythmia \n2.  All post-surgical RHD should be on penicillin prophylaxis.",
