  {
    "id": 215,
    "text": "56\n \n1-6 years: \no Renal vascular diseases \no Renal parenchymal diseases (glomerulonephritis, hemolytic-\nuremic syndrome…) \no Coarctation of the aorta \no Medications (steroids) \no Essential hypertension \no Tumor \n6-15 years: \no Renal vascular diseases \no Renal parenchymal diseases (glomerulonephritis, hemolytic-\nuremic syndrome…) \no Essential hypertension \no Coarctation of the aorta \no Endocrine causes \no Nutritional causes (obesity) \no Tumor (pheochromocytoma) \nSigns and symptoms: \no Oedema, haematuria, proteinuria \no Headache, convulsions, coma and visual symptoms \no Acute heart failure and pulmonary oedema \no Acute respiratory distress,  \no Some children may be asymptomatic",
    "source": "IMB-NCDs-guideline",
