  },
  {
    "id": 235,
    "text": "77\n \n \nThe following factors need to be considered: \no Age, sex \no Nature and severity of lesion  \no Risks related to anticogalution (warfarin) & pregnancy \no Follow-up: anticoagulation issues including availability and \nproximity of tests and medications, education level,  \ncompliance to follow up, social problems… \no Patient preference and informed consent?? Number of \nchildren? Contraception?",
