    "id": 236,
    "text": "78\n \n4.2.1 POSTOPERATIVE COMPLICATIONS \no Major bleeding: needing re-intervention  \no Arrhythmias ( A-V block…): needing temporary or permanent \npacemaker !! \no Heart failure: needing heart failure management \no Inflammation: \no Pericardial effusion \no Pleural effusion  \no Infections: \no wound infection, mediastinitis \no Infective endocarditis  \no Others: depending of the type of surgery (pneumothorax, \ncheloid scar…)  \no Wound infection, post op period \nFigure 1: Wound infection, post op period",
