    "text": "105\n \n5.2.7.3 Use the step method \nIntermittent\nPersistent - Mild\nPersistent - Moderate\nPersistent - Severe\nASTHMA ATTACK\nStep-up therapy\nWhen patient’s \nasthma severity \nworsen\nStep-down therapy\nWhen the  patient \nachieves 3 months \nof symptom relief",
