  {
    "id": 264,
    "text": "111\n \n5.2.11 MEDICATION ADHERENCE  \nEvaluate the patient’s ability to follow the treatment plan from last \nvisit. \n5.2.12 IDENTIFY THE TREATMENT STEP  \nIntermittent\nPersistent - Mild\nPersistent - Moderate\nPersistent - Severe\nASTHMA ATTACK\nStep-up therapy\nWhen patient’s \nasthma severity \nworsen\nStep-down therapy\nWhen the  patient \nachieves 3 months \nof symptom relief\n \n***Once the correct treatment step is identified check section \n5.2.8 and develop a treatment plan***",
