  {
    "id": 278,
    "text": "127\n \n6.2.5.3 Type of Diabetes  \nBased on the information gathered in the exam, decide whether the patient has: \nType 1 Diabetes\nType 2 Diabetes\nMixed Diabetes (Malnutrition)\n \n \n6.2.5.4 Determining Next Steps \nTo know whether the patient should be transferred to the district hospital or started \non treatment, choose the appropriate next step below by considering their glucose \ncontrol and danger signs:",
