  {
    "id": 282,
    "text": "131\n \n6.2.7 ROUTINE INVESTIGATIONS \n   EVERY VISIT \n   EVERY 6 \nMONTHS \n   ANNUALLY \n   EVERY YEAR \n Random or \nFasting \nFingerstick \n HbA1c \n Monofilament \nTest \n Refer for \nOphthalmolo\ngic Exam \n Weight and BP \n Urine Protein \nwith Dipstick \n Creatinine \n Foot Exam \n  \n6.2.8 FOLLOW-UP SCHEDULE \n \nGood Glycemic Control \nPoor Glycemic Control \nOral \nmedication \nstarted or changed \nNA \nReturn in 2-4 weeks \nInsulin started or \nchanged \nNA \nReturn in 1-2 weeks \nNo \nMedication \nChange \nReturn in 3 months \nNA",
