    "id": 284,
    "text": "133\n \n \n6.3 The Follow-up Patient Visit \nThis section emphasizes a systematic approach, which will helpyou:  \n1.Assess medication adherence; and 2. Assess glucose control. \n1. History  (See 6.2.1) \n2. Vital Signs  (See 1.1.1) \n3. Physical Exam  (See 1.1.1) \n4. Lab Review  (See 6.2.4) \n \nUse the same information from \nthe initial visit for HISTORY, \nVITAL SIGNS, PHYSICAL EXAM \nand LAB REVIEW in the follow \nup visit.",
