    "text": "165\n \n7.2.6 LABORATORYAND IMAGING REVIEW \nLAB/Imaging  REQUEST \nWHEN \nCREATININE \no Initial visit; \no 6 months then yearly;  \no It can be checked at any visit if \npatients presents signs and \nsymptoms \nURINE DIPSTICK FOR PROTEIN \no Every visit \nUREA \no Initial visit \no 6months the yearly \nHEMOGLOBIN \no Every 6 months \no It can be checked at any visit if \nsigns of anemia(palor,fatigue) \nHIV \no Initial visit \nGLYCEMIA \no Initial visit \nPOTASSIUM \no Every visit(especially when on \nACEI treatment , oliguria,anuria) \nHEPATITIS B AND C SCREENING o Initial visit \nRenal \nultrasound, \nrenal \nstructure \n(cortex \nand \nmedullar) \no where available",
